"""``gml serve`` — FastAPI HTTP surface for the orchestration layer.

Endpoints:

  POST /chat              — one-shot chat turn; returns TurnResult JSON
  POST /chat/stream       — same turn, but streams the response text via
                            Server-Sent Events
  GET  /memories          — list persisted memories (paginated)
  POST /memories          — add a memory manually
  GET  /health            — liveness
  GET  /metrics           — Prometheus text format

The server keeps Conversation objects per session_id in process memory and
shares one Pipeline+MemoryStore across sessions. Restart-safe: memory
lives on disk in JSONL.

Run:
    gml serve --port 8000 --target deepseek
"""
